{"tid":2376332,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"被素食主義者要求別再吃動物的肉！「地獄廚神」戈登直接回嗆：大蠢蛋！","createTime":"2021-01-22T16:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T00:37:09.000Z","uid":372131,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1b19a65949c174e2ac57bd633787110fb62545","tid":2376332,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"今年 54 歲的蘇格蘭廚師戈登拉姆齊（Gordon Ramsay）以料理選秀節目《地獄廚房》（Hell's Kitchen）中憤怒主廚導師形象走紅於全球，他旗下的餐廳更曾累計獲得過十八顆米其林星之多，專業形象完美勝過另一位電視名廚：Jamie Oliver 示範炒飯「加果醬」又拿去沖冷水，網友狂噓：看起來像噴。不過當戈登碰上「素食議題」之時，這位料理過無數肉品的名廚又會如何回應呢？<br />\n<br />\n▼「地獄廚神」戈登以熱愛在推特上親自與各國粉絲互動聞名，通常大家都會分享自己料理的影片或照片，請這位世界級的廚師來評論自己的餐點看起來如何並打分數。不僅有人會想藉此獲得戈登的讚美，也有人是專門想討「地獄廚神」罵自己幾句。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gordonramsay/status/1351180597956399104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgordonramsay%2Fstatus%2F1351180597956399104%3Fs%3D21&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5B5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=acc0265a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgordonramsay%2Fstatus%2F1351180597956399104%3Fs%3D21&h=f1443eef\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gordonramsay/status/1351180597956399104?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nSource：twitter@GordonRamsay<br />\n<br />\n不過沒想到現在就有一名銀髮女性用烏克麗麗自彈自唱，創作了一首名為〈Eating animals is wrong gordon ramsay〉的歌曲，企圖用歌聲來感化戈登而唱道：「吃動物是錯誤的～戈登拉姆齊～傷害動物是錯誤的～戈登拉姆齊～分享這首歌，即使你叫我小蠢蛋也沒關係，只要你從此成為素食者～ 」<br />\n沒想到地獄廚神戈登一邊看影片一開始吃菜，後來直接拿出一整個大牛肉漢堡嗑起來，並回嗆影片中的素食女性：「素食大蠢蛋！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdyyGDR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdyyGDR.jpg&h=773b00b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：TheGamerPro4356@YOUTUBE<br />\n▼下方影片中可以聽見這位素食主義者唱的是：「即使你叫我 Donut 也沒關係。」這是因為甜甜圈中間有一個洞，可以用來形容一個人腦洞或愚蠢的意思，因此「地獄廚神」戈登時常會用：「You Donut！」罵失誤的參賽者，這也是這位素食女性提起這個字眼的原因，不過沒想到她的不吃肉主張只換來戈登一句簡單回嗆，呈現出一位廚師被素食主義者念煩了的心情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WbC4qt9ydTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWbC4qt9ydTY&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5B5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=bbcc32f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WbC4qt9ydTY</a><br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://today.line.me/tw/v2/article/QWKyEe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Ftw%2Fv2%2Farticle%2FQWKyEe&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5B5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=e4326374\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/tw/v2/article/QWKyEe</a><br />\n<br />\n素食撚又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c035ac1d949603d8dce58923181312f485f283","tid":2376332,"uid":200083,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"點解呢啲食齋柒頭永遠個樣都奇撚怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfedf42c33caba3f5df7f8d03cf43dbd2c202bc1","tid":2376332,"uid":76216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"叫廚師食素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33075bd69f25cf4f436458ac43426a9738cfe198","tid":2376332,"uid":20984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"49c035ac1d949603d8dce58923181312f485f283","tid":2376332,"uid":200083,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"點解呢啲食齋柒頭永遠個樣都奇撚怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"營養不良"},{"pid":"c201ced72ebe3d119a8726e6ab223a70aeaacc7f","tid":2376332,"uid":117276,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"食素唔係問題<br />\n但唔可以逼人食<br />\n左膠唔識尊重人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6aa54f0e0ae621d0f829fa0dba673224e57f10","tid":23